Spinister leads the way for Needlenose, and bursts into the huge bay
holding the Constructicons creation. Hook soars out of the engine hold,
where he had just finished installing the hyperdrive. He landed, and
dosted off his hands. "Done. Anything else Scrapper?" he asked.
